Not much was left of Fleming's beautiful warship after our victory. It is off to join the other wrecks of the seas. That should give the navy a good blow. But they shouldn't be our biggest concern for now. My navigator reports an unusual sighting, a ship with old grey sails, as big as Fleming's warship. It flies no flag and is travelling according to the course on the treasure map. I get the feeling that Silver's ship is not a wreck on the bottom of the sea after all, but a ghost ship, doomed to sail this course forever. Forever, or until we have freed it from its prey.
->endScene

