So this is it at last. The end of our long journey is finally in sight and I'm already imagining all the things I'm going to buy with all that gold. Many of my men can hardly contain their excitement either. The last battle. The last hurdle to a life of freedom and prosperity. We're all going to set sail, far away from the navy and other pirates. On a peaceful and joyful island. A dream worth fighting for, a dream that will become reality after this battle. For freedom, for prosperity, for victory! Attack!
